{"tid":872990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵落馬洲站女子墮軌　消防到場拯救","createTime":"2018-10-23T06:14:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-23T07:27:17.000Z","uid":132137,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b56cf7d9fccd0888a853b600656d15d3db2dc712","tid":872990,"uid":132137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T06:14:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181023/bkn-20181023132606914-1023_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181023%2Fbkn-20181023132606914-1023_00822_001.html&d=sQ4YyRmqG3u9s5iFVk398C7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=3910c814\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181023/bkn-20181023132606914-1023_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n港鐵東鐵線有人墮軌，今日(23日)中午1時14分，落馬洲站一名女子跌落路軌遭駛至列車撞倒，倒臥路軌中被困車底受傷。港鐵職員見狀立即報警求助，消防接報到場設法將女事主救出，警方在場調查翻看月台閉路電視影片，追查女子墮軌原因。"},{"pid":"36c0b5e3f2a04621a6df5089c0dd56566231a87f","tid":872990,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T06:15:55.000Z","msg":"大肚婆？"},{"pid":"b5dc2f8a1f9aa2de77182f9bcb4ff86f380de2b6","tid":872990,"uid":132137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T06:22:46.000Z","msg":"好似愈黎愈密<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9656014425f64c7bdee6d882fcb23def1645ef77","tid":872990,"uid":193364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T06:26:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 死定傷"},{"pid":"7759c3e22314ce8825a02c90b340f3e3639dc2ab","tid":872990,"uid":38216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T07:27:17.000Z","msg":"好彩係1點發生嘅事"}]}